                                    <q xml:lang="gez">እሴብሕ፡ ጸጋኪ፡ ኦዑጽፍተ፡ ልብሰ፡ ወርቅ፡ ንግስትየ፡ ወለተ፡ ዳዊት፡ ንጉሥ።</q>
                                </item>
                                
                                <item xml:id="a11">
                                    <locus from="178v"/>
                                    <desc type="GuestText">
                              <title ref="LIT2833RepCh117" type="complete"/>. The following is the incipit:</desc>
